BOWER NOTES

installing bower--------------------
    1)install npm, git
    2)npm install -g bower


installing a package!---------------
    1)go to the project dir
    2)bower install jquery
    3)to save to the JSON while installing, "bower install jquery -S"
installing with a version----------
    1)bower install jquery#1.2.2

listing all paths------------------
    bower list --paths

uninstalling------------------------
    bower uninstall jquery

creating bower.js Filter
      bower init

Installing packages using bower.JSON
      bower install
